---
// InstallSection — WP-05 scaffold stub, WP-08 fills in.
//
// Reserved layout for the point-of-intent install beat: the app download
// matrix (Downloads.astro), the scripted one-liner (InstallBlock.astro), and
// the skills on-ramp (`npx skills add ...`). All of that content lives in
// the CURRENT src/pages/index.astro today and is copy-accounted in WP-05's
// report as "moved to WP-08 scope" — nothing here is invented, this section
// only reserves the seam WP-08 builds into.
//
// Anchors kept live now (not stubbed) because the hero's ghost row
// (MomentHero) already links to them:
//   - #install → "Download ↓"
//   - #skills  → "Or start with a skill"
// so those two ids exist on this stub even before WP-08 lands the real
// content, otherwise the hero links dangle.
//
// Tone: light (parchment pole) per the D-01 narrative — this section sits
// between the light packages teaser and the dark Obi section (WP-05 keeps
// the light tone for the seam WP-08 designs against).
---

<section class="sk-section" data-tone="light" id="install">
	<div class="sk-wrap">
		<!-- WP-08 -->
		<div class="stub-box" aria-hidden="true">
			<p class="stub-box__label">Install — reserved for WP-08</p>
			<p class="stub-box__note">
				Download matrix, install one-liner, and skills on-ramp land here
				(lifted from the current production index.astro, claims verbatim).
			</p>
		</div>
		<span id="skills" aria-hidden="true"></span>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.stub-box {
		border: 1px dashed var(--site-border-strong);
		border-radius: var(--radius-lg, 10px);
		padding: var(--space-8, 32px) var(--space-6, 24px);
		text-align: center;
		color: var(--site-faint);
	}
	.stub-box__label {
		font-family: var(--site-font-mono);
		letter-spacing: 0.14em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		margin: 0 0 var(--space-2, 8px);
	}
	.stub-box__note {
		margin: 0;
		max-width: 46ch;
		margin-inline: auto;
		font-size: 0.9375rem;
	}
</style>
